text: José Manuel Pinillo (8 March 1902 - 8 September 1968) was a Spanish swimmer. He competed in two events at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1902 births Category:1968 deaths Category:Spanish male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Spain Category:Swimmers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Seville
